Visval – Massive Series
Massivemessenger looking casually sophisticated with this With vintage looks with modern functionality. It is really great for daily pack. Features include internal sleeve that fits a 14 inch laptop sleeve, zippered front pocket and 2 sided utility pocket

Specification:
• Dimensions: 38 x 30 x 16 cm
• Fabric: Poly-Fabric / Faux Leather

Details :
• Nice faux leather shoulder straps
• Internal padded sleeve fits 14" laptop
• One large main compartment Zippered
• 1 front zippered pocket
• 1 sleeve pocket on the back
• Secondary pocket on the front and 2-sided small pocket
• Fully padded back panel
• Adjustable padded shoulder straps
